---
description: "Simple model selection (GPT-3.5 vs GPT-4o)"
globs:
  - "src/**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Backend endpoints accept `model: "gpt-3.5" | "gpt-4o"`.
- **Teacher Bas**: default 3.5; 4o allowed until monthly quota; then silent fallback to 3.5 + subtle notice.
- **Pro/School**: default 4o; fallback to 3.5 if 4o quota depleted.
- UI: a single Swedish toggle/dropdown: **Standard (GPT-3.5)** / **Avancerad (GPT-4o)**; remember last choice; avoid jargon.
- Telemetry: chosen model & fallback events.